job.title: UPSC CMS Exam Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 838 vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:838

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Assistant Divisional Medical Officer, General Duty Medical Officer 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for MBBS pass has been published by Union Public Service Commission for General Duty Medical Officer vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of General Duty Medical Officer, from 07-07-2021, and till 27-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for all category candidates is only Rs. 200/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a General Duty Medical Officer in UPSC, your MBBS must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 07-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 27-07-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

UPSC General Duty Medical Officer Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for UPSC CMS Exam Recruitment 202? 

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the General Duty Medical Officer. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of UPSC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by UPSC
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
